      },
      "timestamp": "17:48",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "那很好了，我写了一下午修改意见和教案，刚刚准备去吃饭，应该和砂锅排骨无缘了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:52",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？这么忙啊，我以为当了老师之后会很清闲呢……",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我之前也因为这个还考虑要不要往讲师这方面努努力，毕竟可是双休和带薪寒暑假！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:53",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "感觉超爽的！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:54",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "其实不然。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:55",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "恰恰相反。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:55",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然说没有忙到脚不沾地，但备课，写教案，项目申报书和论文指导，还有职称评定的事情……",
